  <entry>
    <title>AI is accelerating cyberattacks—here’s how to stay ahead</title>
    <link href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/microsoft-entra-blog/ai-is-accelerating-cyberattacks%E2%80%94here%E2%80%99s-how-to-stay-ahead/4528592" rel="alternate"/>
